<h1>PDFjs Viewer Demo</h1>
<h3>Installation</h3>
<p><b>Add this line to your application's Gemfile:</b></p>
<p><b>gem 'pdfjs_rails'</b></p>
<p><b>And then execute:</b></p>
<p><b>$ bundle</b></p>
<p><b>$ rails g pdfjs_rails:install</b></p>

